entries.journal_entry_description: There are plenty of people in Mos Eisley willing to trade their soul for a few credits. There are even more willing to trade someone else's for the same. Aigorn seems to be one of the latter. If you help her you will undoubtedly be well paid... but at what cost?
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You have been contacted by a Trandoshan named Aigorn. She knows you are working with Reimus and has offered you a better deal. She wants to sell the data to the highest bidder. You both stand to collect quite a bit of money, even if it does cost a few lives.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return the medical research data to Aigorn.
